name: CybrPets : IM NOT THE HERO
blurb: EXPLORE, TRAIN, AND BATTLE with your CybrPet.. Your journey begins here....join our hero in a world of Epic adventures

rewards.reward: Congratulations you are officially part of the team, and you shall be treated as such. Take a hop step over to the official CybrPets site and find your place on the Wall of Fame
Not only can you proudly brag about your Wall of Fame achievement, but you will also get an Exclusive CybrPets Kickstarter Wallpaper!!!!
HeadStart: A copy of the game and Early access to the game's Beta. This will give you an early preview of your name as a Sponsor in the Game's Credits

Leading the Lap: So now you have The Game, Saw your name in the Credits of the Game.... Now is time to wear your shirt with pride!! ... thats right when people compliment your new shirt...  2 Thumbs pointed at yourself you can tell them you Made it possible.

Finish Line in Sight: an Exclusive Limited edition hand drawn sketch by the game's lead artist. + All rewards listed above... A copy of the game, Early Access to beta, Sponsor Credits in the game, and A Spiffy CybrPets Shirt!!

An Ultra Rare 16x20 Signed Poster Designed and Drawn by the lead artist and Signed by the Entire Production Team Behind CybrPets, and all previous Rewards; A copy of the game, Early Access to beta, in Game Sponsor Credits, and an Exclusive Hand Drawn Sketch.

Victory Lap: An Exclusive KickStarter Only Shirt designed for this event, which means you will never see this shirt anywhere else and to go along with this you will receive executive producer Credits in game!!!! be part of history!! + All Previous Rewards

Podium: Name your own CyberPet!!! pick any name you want for your very own CybrPet and we will design a character to be just what you imagined he would look like, a chance to help us on key events in the story and receive production credit, as well as behind the scenes updates on progress on production of the game + All Previous Rewards!!.

Trophy: Here is your chance to See your vision come to life, we will work with you to bring your custom CybrPet to life, we will work with you to design your very own game character and CybrPet, this means you will literally be in the game!!!! + All Previous Rewards.

IM NOT THE HERO: How many times have you played a game and wanted to be the Cool Bad guy at the end of the game? Here is your chance to design our Hero's Rival who will appear in both the Game and Comic. We will work with you to design and name our hero's rival along with his CybrPet and we all know the Bad guys are always the coolest characters. Become part of the Story of CybrPets by creating a key part of it. + All previous Rewards.

IM NOT THE HERO...So WHO AM i? We want you to help us design the hero of our story. Thats Right!! every time someone boots up the game, your character is who they will see. you will be responsible for designing the character that people will grow with throughout this heroic adventure... oh and did we forget to mention you will also help us create his story... thats right you will collaborate with us on creating key aspects of the game.. after all it is your hero we are talking about and you will receive Production level Credits and a Meet and Greet with the Production staff. + All Previous Rewards "excluding Previous IM NOT THE HERO tier"
